{"type": "article", "id": 24116, "title": "这位纽约插画家，擅长绘制中产阶级生活", "description": "商家大多喜欢自信、向上的插画风格。", "date": "2016-03-21T19:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 17633, "name": "插画家"}, {"id": 25114, "name": "商业插画"}, {"id": 117, "name": "纽约"}, {"id": 25115, "name": "画师"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 191, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123047hXPL3db2IR1aKpFl.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p>“中产阶级趣味”很大程度上是整个社会文化保持趣味的基准啊。他们的精神文化有一些标签式的内容：自驾游、上健身课、登山、度假……在美国，许多插画家都在表现中产阶级这个可爱群体。他们的风格或讽刺或温和，今天我们来介绍笔触比较温和的一个。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://tomiillustration.com/ABOUT\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Tomi Um</a> 是一位老牌的纽约插画家，他的作品简单温暖，绘制的艺术插画常常出现在《华尔街日报》、《纽约时报》、<i>Monocle</i> 等媒体上。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123039KBymj2Le3JOTPtCl.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66712707\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123040ArbuaOJTG3IqZRd0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91712707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123041aANHshqDdLk7bJF9.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Tomi Um: 《哈利的五点钟》（Harry’s Five O’Clock）</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123041acUCFs9RPk0Hl3Nr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79972376\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《哈利的五点钟》</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123042bQkawqlpciXxW8Ay.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123042vLHyZFluV5a218mz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64779006\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Tomi Um: MIT Review</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031230430hF6ojELRclJkC2I.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是 Tomi Um 发表在《华尔街日报》上的作品，现代生活</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123043mkK863u7LjCF1JEb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.90055249\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>除了艺术插画，Tomi Um  还绘制过不少商业插画，从古根海姆博物馆到哈利剃须刀，他的客户范围极其广泛。</p>\n<p>讲到这里，有必要介绍一下商业插画。所谓的商业插画，是指画家为一家厂商服务，一旦商家支付了费用，画家便放弃了作品的所有权，但他可以得到比例较高的报酬。商业插画通常有很强的艺术魅力和表现力，但它们的使用寿命也比较短——当一个商品或企业进行更新换代时，插画的生命也就结束了。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://tomiillustration.com/ABOUT\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Tomi Um</a> 的作品整洁、自信、向上，这种风格为他赢得了不少的客户， 2009 年至今，他的作品也被多次展出。</p>\n<p class=\"\">以下是 Tomi Um 为厂商绘制的部分商业插画：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123044tE4PLZaUAyiXwWoR.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65469613\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">为 Harry 剃须刀绘制的商业插画</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123045l2ECnHjkBhrimcfo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.395\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是他为 Fab.com 绘制的商业插画，介绍了订购沙发的过程</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">更多作品，可以移步至 <a href=\"http://tomiillustration.com\">Tomi Um 本人的官方网站</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123045fQMgaKkbXW2EujJe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123046S56gIqcoKVM0Qja2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031230467a0dWJVrPoZMU3f4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/tomi-um-modern-life-tidy-lines-170316\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">itsnicethat</a><br></p>\n\n\n"}